title: DDFP 413: Week 15 Preview & Star Wars
itunes:title: DDFP 413: Week 15 Preview & Star Wars
description:
Shek sits down with NFL Media's Alex Gelhar and Matt Franciscovich to make their Week 15 "Red Challenge Flag Picks". The guys also talk Star Wars, Cam Newton, and Eddie Lacy. Lastly, Shek prepares for his trip to New York with Odell Beckham Jr. Watch the full show here https://youtu.be/gI8oO1Q-T6k
